OL,6,FMothers who struggled in the
OL,7,F'sweltering' heat on Homerton
OL,8,FHospital's maternity unit share their
OL,9,Fstories with ITV News London's Carolyn
OL,10,FSim
OL,12,FBaby Airah was born eleven weeks ago.
OL,13,FAfter a complicated birth, all his mum
OL,14,FGeri wanted to do was rest and enjoy
OL,15,Fher son.
OL,17,FBut instead, she was stuck on an
OL,18,Fovercrowded, noisy ward in unbearable
OL,19,Fheat, with bright lights overhead.
