OL,3,C800 mothers share 'traumatic'
OL,4,Cexperience on Homerton ward
OL,6,FGeri is among over eight hundred women
OL,7,Fwho've shared what they describe as
OL,8,Ftraumatic experiences inside Homerton
OL,9,FHospital's maternity unit.
OL,11,FSome have said that in the summer
OL,12,Fmonths - the temperature can reach 40
OL,13,Fdegrees Celsius.
OL,15,FThey've seen mothers and midwives
OL,16,Ffainting - and babies struggling to
OL,17,Ffeed.
OL,19,FFormer Homerton patient, Geri Spicer,
OL,20,Fsaid: "It was so hot and honestly you
OL,21,Ffelt a bit sick because it was so hot.
