OL,6,F"When I was told that I'd have to
OL,7,Fspend a few more days there I actually
OL,8,Fhad a bit of a breakdown in the
OL,9,Fhospital because I had no natural
OL,10,Flight, I couldn't breathe, I felt like
OL,11,Fthere was no air and for me personally
OL,12,Fhaving had an emergency c-sec and
OL,13,Fhaving had quite a traumatic birth it
OL,14,Fwasn't conducive to healing, bonding
OL,15,Fwith my baby in any way because it's a
OL,16,Freally difficult environment to be in."
OL,18,F6000 women give birth at Homerton
OL,19,Fevery year.
