OL,6,FAn inspection by the Care Quality
OL,7,FCommission last year found that 85 per
OL,8,Fcent of maternity patients they spoke
OL,9,Fto had complaints.
OL,11,FIt's been an issue for almost a decade.
OL,13,FNow, two women have launched a
OL,14,Fpetition demanding improvements.
OL,16,FUntil yesterday Deborah Sayagh was in
OL,17,Fcharge of getting patient feedback in
OL,18,Fthe maternity unit.
