OL,3,C800 mothers share 'traumatic'
OL,4,Cexperience on Homerton ward
OL,6,FHomerton Hospital told ITV News London
OL,7,Fthat it is aware of the issues and are
OL,8,Fworking to resolve them.
OL,10,FIt has installed air conditioning
OL,11,Funits on the ward during the summer
OL,12,Fmonths and temperatures are constantly
OL,13,Fmonitored.
OL,15,FA spokesperson say they are planning
OL,16,Fto ask for resources to expand and
OL,17,Fmodernise the ward but that would
OL,18,Fdepend on substantial investment.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G7/10
