OL,3,C800 mothers share 'traumatic'
OL,4,Cexperience on Homerton ward
OL,6,FThe hundreds of mothers who signed the
OL,7,Fpetition believe that putting things
OL,8,Fright is of vital importance.
OL,10,FAnd many, like Geri, say they wouldn't
OL,11,Fgo back there to have another baby.
OL,13,FA CQC spokesperson said: "Since our
OL,14,Flast inspection, people have told us
OL,15,Fof their concerns around high
OL,16,Ftemperatures on Homerton University
OL,17,FHospital's maternity wards. We have
OL,18,Fmet with the trust to discuss the
OL,19,Factions they are taking to address
OL,20,Fthese issues to make sure mothers and
OL,21,Fbabies are comfortable.
