OL,6,F"We're assured that the trust is
OL,7,Ftaking appropriate action to address
OL,8,Fthe issue, including the installation
OL,9,Fof new air conditioning and better
OL,10,Fmonitoring of temperatures.
OL,12,F"We'll continue to monitor the service
OL,13,Fand the progress of these improvements
OL,14,Fto ensure they are fully implemented
OL,15,Fand maintained.
